@startuml FindByPage

actor User
participant "BaseServiceImpl" as BSI
participant "ValidationUtils" as VU
participant "Repository" as REP

== Find By Page ==
User -> BSI: findByPage(page, size, sortBy, sortDir, dtoClass)
activate BSI

BSI -> VU: Validate page request parameters
activate VU
VU --> BSI: Validation complete
deactivate VU

BSI -> REP: Find entities by page
activate REP
REP --> BSI: Page of entities
deactivate REP

loop Convert each entity to DTO
    BSI -> BSI: Call convertToDTO(entity)
    note right: convertToDTO được triển khai trong lớp con
end

BSI --> User: Return Page of DTOs
deactivate BSI

@enduml
